attributes.title: My breakfast
attributes.description:
Created on August 25, 2010 by leila on Sourcemap.org:

After making this map I started to think more about food that I buy and eat. As you will see food that I have in my kitchen comes from Slovenia, Bosnia, Croatia, Italy and Switzerland.

attributes.name: Milk 1l Alpsko mlijeko
attributes.title: Milk 1l Alpsko mlijeko
attributes.description: The year 1967 is the year the Alpine milk was “born”, and in more than 3 decades it became a synonym for quality long life milk. It was the first milk of its kind in Slovenia and, of course, the entire ex-Yugoslavia.
